name: Sunset Skull Earring
description:
This earring is a lot like the Tropical Sunset Clip. It has fuschia pink and orange schlappen feathers, but it topped with white & ginger saddle feathers that give it an overall different look. Fitted onto antique silver chain, it is topped with a white Howlite Skull. Perfect for any hair colour or length! 

THIS SEASON MUST HAVE! 

Not all feathers look the same. This means that each piece will be as unique as their owner. 


Photographed by: James Milne

name: Peacock Tail Clip
description:
As the name suggests the clip is inspired by a Peacock's Tail. The feathers fade from a beautiful jade green to turquoise blue and finally purple. The top is accented with two peacock eyes. Fitted onto silver & bronze chain, it includes 2 white Howlite Cross charms and finished with a crocodile clip for secure wear. Perfect for any hair length or colour!
Available in: LONG or SHORT. 

MUST HAVE FOR THIS SEASON!

Not all feathers look the same. This means that each piece will be as unique as their owner. 


Photographed by: James Milne
